USB Connectors
--------------

There are 2 x **USB HOST** and 1 x **USB DEVICE** (for flashing OS) ports onboard: |USB|, as shown in the figures below.

.. warning::

  **Please unplug USB mouse/keyboard** from the USB3.0 port when flashing OS.

|usb_usbc_conflict|

.. rst-class:: text-center

  |USBA_img|

  *USB HOST Ports*

  |USBC_img|
  
  *USB Type-C Port*

